UMEME celebrates Women’s Day with refugee women

As the World celebrated the International Women’s day, the ladies from UMEME and the Uganda Electricity Distribution Company Ltd were out to meet these wretched of the earth.

Refugees depend on handouts usually from international agencies. However, this support in most cases is never enough, forcing, especially the women refugees to use all kinds of methods to fend for their families. 

As the World celebrated the International Women’s day, the ladies from UMEME and the Uganda Electricity Distribution Company Ltd were out to meet these wretched of the earth. 

Find out what transpired at the power engagement with refugee women in Nsambya, a Kampala suburb in Her Vision.